# Specific File Patterns to Ignore

# Allow hardcoded values in test configurations
**/src/test/**/TestModels.kt
**/src/test/**/BaseIntegrationTest.kt
**/src/test/**/WebAuthnTestHelpers.kt

# Allow debug mode in development scripts
**/start-dev.sh
**/start-full.sh
**/debug/

# Allow localhost origins in development configurations
**/webauthn-server/docker-compose*.yml
**/web-test-client/src/webauthn-client.ts

# Exclude vulnerability tracking files (they're meant to contain security info)
**/vulnerability-tracking.json
**/security-scan-results.json

# Exclude Dependabot configuration (it's meant to manage dependencies)
**/.github/dependabot.yml

# Performance measurement scripts (may have relaxed security for testing)
**/scripts/performance/
**/scripts/testing/

# GitHub Actions workflows (different security model)
**/.github/workflows/

# Exclude semgrep rules themselves from analysis
**/semgrep-rules/
**/.semgrepignore

# Custom Ignores for WebAuthn Specific Patterns

# Allow test credentials service to have relaxed security (it's for testing only)
**/webauthn-test-credentials-service/src/main/kotlin/com/vmenon/webauthn/testservice/

# Allow development environment configurations
**/ide.env
**/local.properties
**/setup-secure-env.sh

# Exclude monitoring and debugging utilities
**/scripts/debug/
**/scripts/monitoring/